Class XMLMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.docgene.model.XMLMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.docgene.model.Alignment, ParagraphElement, StyledElement

    public class XMLMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParagraphElement, org.docgene.model.Alignment
    Represent the reference to a Map. Currently only OpenStreetMap maps are allowed
